A cyberpunk cityscape at night where streams of glowing cyan data packets flow through transparent tubes like a vast pneumatic system, fragmenting and reassembling as they travel between towering dark servers. The packets appear as small luminous cubes that break apart into smaller pieces mid-transit, then reform on the receiving end. Neon pink and electric blue accent lights illuminate the industrial infrastructure. Rain-slicked surfaces reflect the data streams below. In the foreground, a massive crystalline funnel collects scattered data fragments, organizing them into orderly queues before sending them onward through the network of pipes. The atmosphere is moody and technological, with steam rising from vents and holographic displays showing flowing waveforms. No human figures present, focusing entirely on the mechanical poetry of data in motion.
